**Explanation of Assembly Order:**

The assembly instructions follow a bottom-up approach. First, place the two base triangular blocks (10 and 11).  Then, the central green block (2) is placed. Finally, the top two triangular blocks (10 and 11) complete the structure.  The order is crucial to maintain structural stability.
